# Stock Market Prediction Web App using Machine Learning

**Stock Market Prediction** Web App based on **Machine Learning** and **Sentiment Analysis** of **News** (API keys included in code). The App forecasts stock prices of the next seven days for any given stock under **NASDAQ** or **NSE** as input by the user. Predictions are made using three algorithms: **ARIMA, LSTM, Linear Regression**. The Web App combines the predicted prices of the next seven days with **real-time sentiment analysis of news** to provide a recommendation whether the price is going to rise or fall.

![Stock Market Prediction](https://github.com/your-username/Stock-Market-Analysis-and-Prediction/blob/main/assets/banner.png)

